# Dune UI Foundation Skill Requirement

For this project, always use the `dune-ui-foundation` skill before implementing changes, updates, or enhancements.

## Required behavior

1. Read `~/.cursor/skills/dune-ui-foundation/SKILL.md` at the start of implementation tasks.
2. Follow the foundation guidance in `reference.md` for styling, animation, and interaction-state decisions.
3. Keep new UI changes consistent with the established catalog unless the user explicitly requests an intentional deviation.

## Scope

This applies to all feature work, refinements, and maintenance updates in this repository.
